<sentence id="4">Because insertion mutations in phoP are polar on phoQ , we constructed strains that expressed the PhoQ protein in the <scope type="neg" id="2"><cue type="neg" id="2">absence</cue> of PhoP</scope> to test <scope type="spec" id="3"> <cue type="spec" id="3">whether</cue> resistance to defensin requires only the phoQ gene product</scope> .</sentence>
<sentence id="5">We found that resistance to defensin requires the function of both components of this regulatory system , because strains expressing PhoQ <scope type="neg" id="4"><cue type="neg" id="4">without</cue> PhoP</scope> were still markedly sensitive to defensins .</sentence>
