<sentence id="7">We also tested for the ability of defensins NP-1 , NP-5 , and HNP-1 to activate pag expression and found that these peptides have <scope type="neg" id="6"><cue type="neg" id="6">no</cue> effect</scope> .</sentence>
<sentence id="8">Defensin resistance is not the only virulence characteristic controlled by the PhoP-PhoQ regulon because mutations in pagC , as well as ones in the phoP locus that resulted in constitutive pag activation ( phenotype PhoPc ) , had <scope type="neg" id="7"><cue type="neg" id="7">no</cue> effect on defensin resistance</scope> , even though they rendered the organism avirulent and deficient in survival within macrophages .</sentence>
